          GitHub</a>
        <a style="text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px;" href="mailto:akashdhaigude1975@gmail.com">ðŸ“§ Gmail</a>
      </div>
      <small>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Akash Dhaigude. All Rights Reserved.</small>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('navToggle').addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.getElementById('navList').classList.toggle('show');
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>